WaveguideLossMeasurement.Name: M22OTE_FCPHA_PDK
WaveguideLossMeasurement.DesignDescription: 2x2 MMI phase test. Compare the output of the ports. Ideally you get a 2x90 degree phase shift. If there is a phase error on that, the MZI spectral response is shifted which corresponds to a phase error (1FSR = 2pi fase error)
